<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10105740>
    dc:description "Figs 986–988. Head incl. antennae/body, lateral view, paratype ♂. (986) Galeopsomyia myrciae; (987) G. myrsineae; (988) G. nana." ;
